에","body":"정작 중요한 가사가 떠오르질 않는다니까.\n{{userName}} 씨, 뭐 좋은 아이디어 없어?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"memorial131-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"타에","body":"……아니지, 갑자기 말해도 안 떠오르려나.\n아하하, 그렇겠네.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"memorial131-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"타에","body":"으~음…… 그냥 가사가 없어도 괜찮으려나?\n복슬복슬~ 폭신폭신~ 이라는 말만 하는 거야. 어때?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"memorial131-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"타에","body":"응, 재미있어 보이지. ……응? \n그 노래를 부를 땐 토끼 인형 옷을 입어…… 보란 말이지.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"memorial131-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"타에","body":"인형 옷…… 응,\n그거 정말 재미있을 것 같아.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"memorial131-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"타에","body":"{{userName}} 씨, 고마워.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"memorial131-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"타에","body":"이번 라이브는 다 같이 인형 옷을 입고 하는 것도 좋을지도 모르겠어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"memorial131-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"타에","body":"폭신한 토끼 인형 옷의 팝핀파.\n응, 귀여워서 좋다.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"memorial131-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"타에","body":"다들 분명 찬성하겠지. 아리사는…… 또 흥흥~하면서\n말하려나?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"mo